      "message": "Yes, all build-xxxx.sh scripts here are used to build prebuilt binaries.\n\ndo_autotools_package means that the package comes with a regular Autoconf-generated \u0027configure\u0027 script, so apply the typical parameters to it (used to select the toolchain, disable shared libraries, etc..)\n\nNOTE: We have prebuilt png because building upstream QEMU2 needs it, even though we use the non-prebuilt version when building the Android QEMU2 version.",
